Building and Running Kismet under Windows/cygwin

Building
--------

Configure using the following options:

./configure --disable-pcap --without-ethereal --disable-gps --disable-wireless \
  --disable-netlink --disable-suid-root
  
Configuration
-------------

Specify the MAC address of the sensor for the capinterface parameter in 
kismet.conf. e.g.

capinterface=00:06:25:02:A8:A2


